There is nothing as such called "Factory Design Pattern" exists. No one has defined or documented such a pattern called Factory, its just a programming convienence of writing the code over which it has became a standard practise of writing Factories.

There are only 2 types of Factory patterns are there
1. Factory Method design pattern
2. Abstract Factory design pattern
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#1 Factory Method design pattern
Across the Factories if we want to acheive standardization in creating object of a Family of related components we need to go for Factory Method design pattern.








